<plot>'Opening the Common Gate' binds together the stories and personal experiences of Indigenous Australians who with humor and grace survived policies that were both draconian and racist. Through personal accounts of storytellers who experienced these times 'Opening the Common Gate' explores citizenship, assimilation, integration and identity.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?414328</url></doc>
